WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Aarti: Hi, I am Aarti, and I will quickly show you how to use Buddhi Align.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:10.000
Aarti: Start on the Home dashboard. Check Daily Rings, then jump into any module.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:15.000
Aarti: In Karma Yoga, I log one action and one impact every day.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Aarti: In Bhakti Journal, I write one reflection and one gratitude point.

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:26.000
Aarti: In Motivation and Analytics, I review streak, totals, and trend charts.

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:31.000
Aarti: In Settings, I manage language, music, and export/import data.

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:36.000
Aarti: As owner, in Admin I review incidents, experiments, audits, and errors.

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:41.000
Aarti: My daily routine is dashboard, two entries, analytics review, and one improvement.

00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:45.000
Aarti: Thanks for watching this quick tour. Let us grow with consistency.
